title: Robert Wyatt - Rock Bottom
description:
Rock Bottom by Robert Wyatt from 1974.





A desert island favourite, unusual and beautiful, already a classic.

There is nothing like "Little Red Riding Hood Hit the Road".
Under intense listening conditions, it takes you apart and puts you back together.



I noticed a lot of good stuff wasn&#039;t available on this site so am putting these albums out there.  Check my others if you like any one of them.



Anybody who is downloading slowly-  it&#039;s not me, it&#039;s you!


: )


Seed when you can!!
